{"tid":1453881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於黑警扮示威者單嘢，大家要醒水","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:01:48.000Z","uid":283049,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2169e218272abd8838755d4562095ed06019cbe7","tid":1453881,"uid":283049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:36:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求求大家唔好捉鬼</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">黑警呢招擺明係想我地互相猜忌</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">千奇不要墮入捉鬼陷阱</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好見到戴耳機就上去砌，據我所知有唔少哨兵都會戴耳機方便互相聯絡</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有內鬼真係唔係啲咩新鮮事，大家喺現場行動時醒水，唔好人地做乜就跟，黑警推進唔好顧住自己跑，你跑得快其他手足跑得慢就會落單</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家一開始捉鬼，場運動基本上玩完</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼開始，左膠就全面進場</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">共勉</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZNB8g1w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNB8g1w.jpg&h=05fce8e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ac9d44815097e0b9d7a9960d7a1b37f849e8375","tid":1453881,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:38:18.000Z","msg":"哦 跑慢d 等俾人捉 其他兄弟就走到啦係咪"},{"pid":"f612c3fd2969c723c99e898677e08b7d377109cc","tid":1453881,"uid":283049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ac9d44815097e0b9d7a9960d7a1b37f849e8375","tid":1453881,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:38:18.000Z","msg":"哦 跑慢d 等俾人捉 其他兄弟就走到啦係咪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:01:48.000Z","msg":"哦<br />\n我以為「齊上齊落」係共識<br />\n原來仲有自私撚只顧自己走仲要理直氣壯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你一個人跑慢啲梗係無用<br />\n我明白見到full gear黑警一嘢衝埋嚟係人都驚，如果成班人可以互相就住大家嘅速度一齊退<br />\n黑警點捉你？班狗衝上嚟想捉人成班人還拖打到班狗後退都得啦<br />\n唔好話成班人 尋晚眼見得2個巴打飛撲上去一拳打埋去都救到個人 有例子㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}